ZH: 新型冠状病毒已经蔓延到全球各地。
EN: The new coronavirus has spread to various parts of the world.

ZH: 这种病毒对老人和小孩尤其危险。
EN: This virus is especially dangerous for the elderly and children.

ZH: 医生们正在全力研究这个病毒的起源。
EN: Doctors are working hard to study the origin of this virus.

ZH: 病毒在空气中传播的速度非常快。
EN: The virus spreads rapidly in the air.

ZH: 请勤洗手和戴口罩以防止病毒传播。
EN: Please wash your hands frequently and wear a mask to prevent the spread of the virus.

ZH: 病毒感染后的症状包括发热和咳嗽。
EN: Symptoms of virus infection include fever and cough.

ZH: 这种病毒对免疫系统造成了重大影响。
EN: This virus has a significant impact on the immune system.

ZH: 世界卫生组织发布了关于这种病毒的最新报告。
EN: The World Health Organization has released the latest report on this virus.

ZH: 政府正采取措施来遏制病毒的传播。
EN: The government is taking measures to control the spread of the virus.

ZH: 预防病毒的最好方法是保持社交距离。
EN: The best way to prevent the virus is to maintain social distance.

ZH: 病毒的来源尚未得到充分确认。
EN: The origin of the virus has not been fully confirmed.

ZH: 爆发初期，病毒传播速度极快。
EN: At the beginning of the outbreak, the virus spread very quickly.

ZH: 病毒可以通过飞沫或接触传播。
EN: The virus can be spread through droplets or contact.

ZH: 需要联合全球努力才能战胜这种病毒。
EN: It will take global efforts to defeat this virus.

ZH: 病毒的变异使得防控变得更加困难。
EN: The mutation of the virus makes prevention and control more difficult.

ZH: 筛查病毒感染者是有效控制传播的手段。
EN: Screening infected individuals is an effective means of controlling the spread.

ZH: 研究人员正试图破译这种病毒的基因序列。
EN: Researchers are trying to decode the genetic sequence of this virus.

ZH: 在全球遍布的实验室中进行着病毒检测工作。
EN: Virus testing is being conducted in laboratories around the world.

ZH: 我们需要加强对病毒的认识和防范意识。
EN: We need to strengthen our understanding and awareness of the virus.
